<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>dead right • dead to rights</xh5><p> <i>dead right</i>—(coll.) absolutely right: You are <u>dead right</u> about the Web connection being the most critical part for a classroom teacher now.</p><p> <i>dead to rights</i>—(in the phrase “catch someone dead to rights”) catch a person in the act of committing a crime: He was caught <u>dead to rights</u> with the goods on him.</p> </entry>
